  "commit_message": "feat: Insert project ID into config after login when cloud provides one (#33976)\n\n* chore: pass remoteOrigin to the cloud on login/signup\n\n* fix(auth): abort browser launch if resetAuthState is called during git-origin lookup\n\nIf the user cancelled while resolveAuthRemoteOrigin() was in flight, the\npending .then() chain would still call auth.start() after the outer promise\nwas already resolved with null. Thread an AbortSignal from #cancelActiveLogin\ninto authApi.logIn/signUp so the gate check in",
